# Browser automation & QA (evidence)

- For user-visible UI flows: use browser-use for interactive verification/screenshots when feasible.
- For scripted E2E-ish flows, scraping, or repeatable checks: use Playwright / webapp-testing / agent-browser.
- For more systematic CLI-driven validation sessions: use qa-tester.

# Output requirement

- Record what you tested as a short checklist and capture key evidence (screenshots/log snippets) when feasible.
